{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The state and progress of an inactive or completed pack are computed lazily. If"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you need the state or progress of a pack whose "},{"code":"state","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property is currently"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"set to "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", observe KVO change notifications on this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pack’s "},{"code":"state","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" key path, then call this method. Alternatively, you can add an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"observer for "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" about this pack that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"come from the default notification center."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/requestprogress"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/requestProgress"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(im)requ